      "present": true,
      "answer": "1.2 Non-Exclusive Grant   You acknowledge and agree that the franchise granted to you hereunder is non-exclusive and is only for one (1) Master Territory; that you are not granted any area, market, or protected territorial rights other than as expressly provided in Section 1.1 of this Agreement; and that you shall not have the right to sublicense, sublease, subcontract or enter into any management agreement providing for the right to operate the Franchised Business or to use the System granted pursuant to this Agreement, except in the manner expressly provided for in Section 5.1 of this Agreement.",
